                                                            'At the start of each battle round after the first, roll a dice. On a 1-4\n                                            nothing happens. On a 5 or 6 the function that currently applies to all\n                                            PENUMBRAL terrain features is replaced with the other function (see\n                                            ‘Repercussions of the Necroquake’).',
